{"tid":675894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母開門1歲兒摔出車外　友人誤踩油門輾爆頭亡 有片","createTime":"2018-05-24T02:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T02:59:38.000Z","uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8588a1b981ab6d9e711459e04ffea63d35aeb6ea","tid":675894,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"苗栗縣頭份市昨深夜發生驚悚的幼童被轎車輾爆頭身亡憾事。蘇姓女子抱著1歲4個月的兒子，搭載王姓男友人的轎車，母子坐前方副駕駛座。蘇女下車買水果，男童在副駕駛座玩耍，未料，媽媽開車門要上車時，男童順勢掉落，王男當時因先打R倒車檔，心急想要拉男童，又不慎誤踩油門，男童遭前方右前輪輾過頭顱，當場爆頭鮮血直流，雖然就近送到距離100多公尺醫院急救，仍傷重不治。警方今天將報請檢察官相驗調查。<br />\n<br />\n頭份警分局交通組長藍忠明說，昨深夜近10時左右，王男開車載蘇女（皆28歲），蘇女並抱著跟前夫生的1歲4個月兒子（姓葉），自新竹市到頭份市遊玩，車子停在自強路、信東路口北上車道，蘇女下車買香蕉，男童在副駕駛座由王男照顧。<br />\n王男向警方說，當時車子未熄火，見蘇女買好水果快上車時，因為車前有別輛車阻擋，先打R檔準備，沒想到男童可能看到媽媽太高興，趴在車門內時，媽媽一打開車門，男童馬上往下墜落，他伸手想要捉人，結果還是沒如願。<br />\n王男說，因為情況危急，他一時緊張，誤將油門當煞車重踩，蘇女尖叫才停車，下車時男童頭部在車底，旁邊地上流了不少鮮血。<br />\n救護車趕抵時，將男童就近送到100多公尺遠的為恭醫院搶救，因頭和胸部傷勢過重，宣告急救無效。警方說，王男沒有酒駕問題，案發前一起到頭份市釣蝦，接著買水果發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180524/1359927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180524%2F1359927&d=h5CBWGnPckCkRoAY9OKbosn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=915de3db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180524%2F1359927&h=eda6da9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180524/1359927</a><br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180524/640_1683893799e766f964e98b0c739e0b4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180524%2F640_1683893799e766f964e98b0c739e0b4b.jpg&h=016bf034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nrip"},{"pid":"78019ec9ee597ed7390e1949ec2a4ecc59efbd99","tid":675894,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔離屋老王?"},{"pid":"e637cf086d615750c33fd360dd90d96f085fc15b","tid":675894,"uid":92743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:37:16.000Z","msg":"屌痴撚線"},{"pid":"1e4f4e732a47f9deb5d907c1d989953abc7d71b0","tid":675894,"uid":80814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"有無咁多巧合呀, 死神不了? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> RIP"},{"pid":"8bb0cd7f81819faaf7e7d0e107eeb708d09739a4","tid":675894,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無咁多巧合呀, 死神來了? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> RIP</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7fd5858480cdf9a4c2c47bba6ba917a0e94665f6","tid":675894,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:38:32.000Z","msg":"伸手就伸手，出乜撚野腳呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52232738059d2cef9525e6a4d8153f84ed19def","tid":675894,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e4f4e732a47f9deb5d907c1d989953abc7d71b0","tid":675894,"uid":80814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"有無咁多巧合呀, 死神不了? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> RIP"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:39:29.000Z","msg":"明顯條細佬阻住司機中出佢老母"},{"pid":"714a3e174cdb67e0edeb26736db4c7f75175f37c","tid":675894,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f52232738059d2cef9525e6a4d8153f84ed19def","tid":675894,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1e4f4e732a47f9deb5d907c1d989953abc7d71b0","tid":675894,"uid":80814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"有無咁多巧合呀, 死神不了? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> RIP"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:39:29.000Z","msg":"明顯條細佬阻住司機中出佢老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:41:36.000Z"